item.title: CVE-2019-6562|2024-08-04T20:23:22.051Z -- philips -- philips%20tasy%20emr
item.description: In Philips Tasy EMR, Tasy EMR Versions 3.02.1744 and prior, the software incorrectly neutralizes user-controllable input before it is placed in output that is used as a web page that is served to other users.
